{"type": "article", "id": 19871, "title": "陀螺灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-29T07:40:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606142525HcVlzbhOmnTNQ9CE.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国建筑师 Ewan Cashman 从陀螺玩具里获得灵感设计了这款灯具，有混凝土制的陀螺状的底座，使得灯也是倾斜站立的，可以 360°旋转。上面连接了木质的灯柱，有点像纺纱针，LED 灯就包裹在里面。这款灯给人一种不稳定的感觉，也激发人们用手去触摸，设计者 Ewan Cashman 正是想让灯具这样的日常用品变得有趣，可以有互动和游戏的心。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150224X6FqGP7EvTgeus5R.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150225uP29N0LfZ8bvCFcX.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150225g1lATFd2bBfRWn0h.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"806\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.86111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150226Q6SMrT4nVgChls9A.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1664\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.77777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}